text: Natalia Didelka Mills Urrunaga (born 22 March 1993) is a Panamanian footballer who plays as a forward for Spanish Segunda División Pro club Fundación Albacete and the Panama women's national team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Panamanian women's footballers Category:Panama women's international footballers Category:Pan American Games competitors for Panama Category:Footballers at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Central American Games bronze medalists for Panama Category:Central American Games medalists in football Category:Segunda División Pro (women) players Category:Panamanian expatriate footballers Category:Panamanian expatriate sportspeople in Spain Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Spain
